bpi.most.client.modules.charts

Class Curve

  • java.lang.Object
    • bpi.most.client.modules.charts.Curve

  • public class Curve
extends java.lang.Object
    Combines the name of a data point with the representation of its series in the chart. Depending on which chart is used, the class of the series is different. The periodicFlag indicates if the data of the series is real time data or periodic generated.

    mike
